title: 2021 XXL Freshman Class Revealed - Official Announcement
author: XXL
description:
Welcome the 2021 XXL Freshman Class. Congratulations 42 Dugg, Iann Dior, Coi Leray, Pooh Shiesty, Flo Milli, Morray, Rubi Rose, Blxst, Toosii, Lakeyah and Freshman 10th spot winner DDG.

#XXLFreshman #XXLFreshmen #2021XXLFreshman #42Dugg #IannDior #CoiLeray #PoohShiesty, #FloMilli #Morray #RubiRose #Blxst #Toosii #Lakeyah

Directed by Travis Satten (www.travissatten.com)
Produced by RiTE Media Group (www.ritemedia.com)

Beat produced by Nick Mira and Humblebee
